<main class="Index">
  <h1 class="Index-welcome"> WELCOME TO COSMOS </h1>
  <div class="Index-front">
    <div class="Index-front_imgContainer">
      <img
        class="Index-front_img"
        src="https://img.freepik.com/foto-gratis/fondo-espacial-polvo-estrellas-estrellas-brillantes-cosmos-colorido-realista-nebulosa-via-lactea_1258-150914.jpg?w=740&t=st=1708265458~exp=1708266058~hmac=50ea48f1e3f374ae2a720b048ccf8f273b7bb1bd0741a09d57f68f843263be12"
        alt="Image of a Cosmos"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="Index-paragraph">
      <h3 class="Index-paragraph_header">
        Take a close look to the infinitum!</h3>
      <p class="Index-paragraph_body">Here in Cosmos you will find a galaxy size of products
        to start your journey to your desired place. You may ask yourself, Â¿How?. Well
        here you will find anything related to your favourites hobbies, games, music, aspirations and
        likings! And to a wonderful price because of our infinity of companies that work with us. <br>

        We really hope you enjoy it.
        <h2 class="Index-paragraph_sign"><strong>- Pedro Alfonzo, some random DS3 player.</strong></h2>
        
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
    <div class="Index-products">
        {{#each products}}
            <div class="Product">
                <div class="Product-container">
                    <img class="Product-container_img" src="{{this.photo}}" alt="{{this.title}}">
                </div>
                <h5 class="Product-name">{{this.title}}</h5>
                <h5 class="Product-price"> ${{this.price}} </h5>
            </div>
        {{/each}}
    </div>
    <span class="Paginate-container">
            {{#if prev}}
                <a
                class="Paginate-prev"
                href="/?title={{filter}}&page={{prev}}"
                >PREV</a>
            {{/if}}
            {{#if next}}
                <a
                class="Paginate-next"
                href="/?title={{filter}}&page={{next}}"
                >NEXT</a>
            {{/if}}
      </span> 
</main>